CHANGELOG
=========
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [2023.6.1] - 2023-06-06
Fix issue with percentile computation

### Add 
- New project structure
- Add bumbver to project

### Fix
- Fix issue with percentile computation (Thank you @Osman Mahmud Kim )
  
## [0.1.0] - 2022-04-27
(Breaking Changes)
### Add
- Add typing to the functions and classes.

## Changed
- Changed the `plot` method in the `Var` class.

## Delete
- Delete the GARCH model. It was very unstable and generated many `NaN` results.
- Delete multi `alpha` support in the `Var` class. It caused multiple problems.
- Delete the term `daily` in the `VaR` class, since you can use every horizon.

## [0.0.5] - 2021-07-11
### Changed
- Add missing files to the distribution (Thank you @Pablo Bartol):
    * requirements.txt
    * README_PYPI.md

## [0.0.3] - 2021-07-11
### Changed
- Add numba in order to speed up the backtest methods.
- Change inefficient code.

## [0.0.2] - 2021-07-01
### Added
- Add new metric `Conditional Drawdown at Risk` (CDaR).
- Add backtest generation, validation and plotting routines.

## [0.0.1] - 2021-06-28
### Added
- Initialized Value-at-Risk package.
- Add the main VaR class.
- Add different models to calculate the VaR.
